There are two types of extended statitics:
table { ll
  Multicolumn statistics ☰ The focus is to gather statistics for sets of → development/databases/Oracle/objects/tables/columns[columns] with correlating values (for example `city` and `state`, or `age` and `income`, or `temperature` and `ice_cream_sales` etc.)
  Expression Statistics ☰
table }

